      <title>南非敦促重新考虑劫持美国办公室的劫机者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-africa-urges-rethink-on-naming-us-office-road-for-hijacker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的总统任期要求约翰内斯堡对命名美国领事馆所在的街道的计划进行限制，这是一名劫持美国客机的巴勒斯坦妇女，因为它试图修补与华盛顿的磨损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-africa-urges-rethink-on-naming-us-office-road-for-hijacker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 15:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
