    <item>
      <title>塔利班在两年多以后释放了美国公民Glezmann</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/us-citizen-glezmann-freed-by-taliban-after-more-than-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务院周四表示，一名被阿富汗塔利班拘留的美国公民已被释放了两年多，因为特朗普政府继续向外国政府施加压力，要求外国政府释放被拘留的美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/us-citizen-glezmann-freed-by-taliban-after-more-than-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 14:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国和意大利摊位欧盟推动为乌克兰施加弹药</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/france-and-italy-stall-eu-push-to-commit-ammunition-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲外交官说，欧盟领导人为获得50亿欧元（54亿美元）的努力，以确保法国和意大利今年为乌克兰提供弹药，这是欧洲外交官的另一个迹象，这是Bloc面孔取代美国对基辅支持的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/france-and-italy-stall-eu-push-to-commit-ammunition-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 14:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟延迟了美国威士忌的50％关税，允许更多谈话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/eu-delays-50-tariffs-on-us-whiskey-allowing-for-more-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将其提议的50％美国威士忌关税推迟到4月中旬，与对美国钢铁和铝关税的更广泛的对齐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/eu-delays-50-tariffs-on-us-whiskey-allowing-for-more-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 12:11:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大与贸易战嘎嘎作响的经济选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/carney-set-to-call-canada-snap-election-for-april-28-globe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）将在几天之内召集全国大选，在该国与美国的贸易战动摇的时候，寻求自己的授权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/carney-set-to-call-canada-snap-election-for-april-28-globe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 09:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国推动乌克兰的维持和平部队的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/uk-spearheads-military-planning-discussions-for-postwar-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方盟友开始谈话，以锤击以盎格鲁 - 法国领导的维持和平部队为基础的详细军事计划，尽管俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝了完整的停火，但仍在为在乌克兰的潜在停战做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/uk-spearheads-military-planning-discussions-for-postwar-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 09:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率，因为关税会加热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美联储应降低利率，并随着官员的关税推动而权衡的经济成本而与美国中央银行分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
